    },
    {
      "start": 548.02,
      "end": 549.08,
      "text": "과시용"
    },
    {
      "start": 549.08,
      "end": 550.72,
      "text": "I'm a ladies man"
    },
    {
      "start": 550.72,
      "end": 552.0,
      "text": "He's a ladies man"
    },
    {
      "start": 552.0,
      "end": 554.62,
      "text": "이처럼 해석하시면 되겠습니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 554.62,
      "end": 557.44,
      "text": "Have you ever been in love?"
    },
    {
      "start": 557.66,
      "end": 559.66,
      "text": "Have you ever been in love?"
    },
    {
      "start": 559.68,
      "end": 560.48,
      "text": "Yes, have you?"
    },
    {
      "start": 560.66,
      "end": 561.92,
      "text": "오, 그럼요"
    },
    {
      "start": 561.92,
      "end": 564.4,
      "text": "사랑에 빠져본 적 있니?"
    },
    {
      "start": 564.64,
      "end": 565.76,
      "text": "라는 질문입니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 565.76,
      "end": 568.1,
      "text": "사랑에 빠져본 적 있으니까"
    },
    {
      "start": 568.1,
      "end": 570.18,
      "text": "우리가 we got married 하겠죠"
    },
    {
      "start": 570.18,
      "end": 572.94,
      "text": "Yeah, 빠져야 가죠"
    },
    {
      "start": 572.94,
